1
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,150 --> 00:01:09,890
[Episode 8]

3
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:13,310
[Yunshao Hall]

4
00:01:13,310 --> 00:01:14,110
Your Majesty,

5
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,510
the painting is here.

6
00:01:15,510 --> 00:01:16,910
I shall take my leave now.

7
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:22,760
Look.

8
00:01:23,090 --> 00:01:24,070
[Xingzhi]

9
00:01:24,070 --> 00:01:25,200
Exactly the same.

10
00:01:25,270 --> 00:01:26,450
[Xingzhi]

11
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,350
Tell me, who is this painter?

12
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:35,120
My mother wasn't from an official family.

13
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:37,110
Why would she appear
in the Imperial Garden?

14
00:01:37,110 --> 00:01:38,200
When did she enter the palace?

15
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,729
And whom did she come to see?

16
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:42,420
I don't know.

17
00:01:44,070 --> 00:01:45,039
Tell me,

18
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:47,000
who exactly is this Xingzhi?

19
00:01:47,050 --> 00:01:49,320
[Xingzhi]

20
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,050
This is my father's courtesy name.

21
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:59,280
The late Emperor?

22
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:01,590
He was fond of calligraphy and painting
during his lifetime.

23
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:05,450
This painting was most likely bestowed
by him upon Grand Tutor Jiang.

24
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:10,430
Then the late Emperor...

25
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:19,520
As I recall,

26
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:23,150
Mother never had any connection
with anyone from the palace,

27
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:25,150
let alone knowing the late Emperor.

28
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:28,090
But the spirit
captured in Mother's portrait

29
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:30,840
speaks of a bond far beyond the ordinary.

30
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,610
Could Mother and the late Emperor have...

31
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,220
Then Xie Jiuzhao and I might be...

32
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:41,630
No, no. That's impossible.

33
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:45,030
If Mother had connections
to the royal family,

34
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:48,240
could there be something
suspicious about her death?

35
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:59,000
Xun Simo, those whom you cannot protect,

36
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,960
I will protect.

37
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,280
Are you trying to make all of us

38
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,470
go down with you?

39
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:04,280
Xie Jiuzhao humiliated me like that,

40
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,280
and you still ask me to endure it.

41
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,000
What am I to you then?

42
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,560
Go get me some wine.

43
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:19,150
General, haven't you
had too much to drink?

44
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:20,140
Stop talking!

45
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,680
If you don't bring it, you're dead.

46
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:23,430
Yes.

47
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:48,750
What brings such an honored guest

48
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:51,000
to my mansion?

49
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,310
Could it be that you've come

50
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,630
to laugh at me too?

51
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,240
Since you're here,

52
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,150
join me for a drink.

53
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:06,870
After all, we're in the same boat.

54
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,750
Your Majesty,

55
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,430
why don't you simply tell

56
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:24,240
Miss Jiang everything about the past?

57
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:27,300
That way, she wouldn't have to
make such a fuss with you.

58
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:36,310
Jiuzhao, don't be afraid.

59
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:41,930
[Young Xie Jiuzhao]

60
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,270
Aunt Liu is here.

61
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,830
No one can hurt you.

62
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:46,560
Mother.

63
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,600
Where have you been?

64
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,580
I've been looking for you all day.

65
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,800
Who are you?

66
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,870
Li.

67
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,040
This is Jiu.

68
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,870
You two will be good friends from now on.

69
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:05,360
Jiu?

70
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,830
Jiu will stay with us at Chunliu Garden

71
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,190
for some time.

72
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,160
You need to take good care of him.

73
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,590
With Mother and me here,

74
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:15,250
no one will dare bully you.

75
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,040
Jiu.

76
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,360
You've completed today's tasks.

77
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,680
You did a great job.

78
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,390
I have a gift for you.

79
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,510
Open your hands.

80
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,120
Mother carved these herself.

81
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,750
One for each of us.

82
00:05:53,430 --> 00:05:54,800
Do only you and I have these?

83
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,920
Of course.

84
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,159
Whenever you see this jade pendant again,

85
00:05:58,159 --> 00:06:01,120
it will mean that someone in this world
is still watching over you

86
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,510
and thinking of you.

87
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,190
I am Li.

88
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:31,390
Three days from now,
I will invite you here for drinks, Zhao.

89
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:32,510
It's a promise.

90
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:49,390
Has all of this

91
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,390
been a mistake all along?

92
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,430
How dare you!

93
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,630
How dare you break into the palace!

94
00:06:58,630 --> 00:07:00,040
Quick! Protect the Emperor!

95
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,800
Yes!

96
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,480
Xun Simo,

97
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,950
you broke into the palace at night.

98
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,430
How many heads do you have to lose?

99
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,560
You corrupt ruler. You stole my bride!

100
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,240
You forced me to this!

101
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,760
After tonight,

102
00:07:26,790 --> 00:07:28,600
everyone will know

103
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,400
you're unworthy of your throne,

104
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:33,870
and I'm ridding the people of a menace.

105
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:36,750
Let me go! Let go!

106
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:40,310
Li, think carefully.

107
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:42,490
He'll soon be dead,

108
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:47,040
and I'll be the great hero of the land!

109
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:49,390
Are you insane?

110
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:53,600
Yes, I am insane.

111
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,190
All because you

112
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,870
betrayed my sincere feelings.

113
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,920
Xun Simo, release Jiang Li.

114
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,300
I will make amends for any grievances.

115
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:05,800
Wait!

116
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,190
Without my command,

117
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,430
no one is to move.

118
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:15,750
Xun Simo,

119
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:18,360
if you leave now,

120
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:21,240
I can pretend none of this happened.

121
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:25,730
You cannot bear the crime of having nine
generations of your clan exterminated!

122
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,830
Kill him!

123
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:32,789
Attack!

124
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,750
Come on then.

125
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:15,690
[Yunshao Hall]

126
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,910
Are you hurt?

127
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,720
No.

128
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,030
Let's go!

129
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:27,790
Imperial guards!

130
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,720
Execute the traitors!

131
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,550
Yes!

132
00:10:38,140 --> 00:10:38,870
[Yunshao Hall]

133
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:52,440
Take him away. Guard him closely.

134
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:55,510
Xie Jiuzhao, you'll die a terrible death!

135
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,120
You'll die a terrible death!

136
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,390
Zhao,

137
00:10:59,470 --> 00:11:00,470
your wound...

138
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:01,670
A terrible death!

139
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:08,630
Zhao!

140
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,120
Zhao!

141
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,960
Zhao.
